ags:resource.dc:title: PCR Analysis about Industrial Structure Adjustment Influencing on Rural Labor Transfer in Liaoning Province

dc:description.dcterms:abstract: Because industrial structure adjustment and rural labor transfer is multifactor variable, we construct a principal component regression model with related data from 1986 to 2010 in this paper. Through the analysis and evaluation using the regression model, we expound the effects that industrial structure adjustment have on the rural labor transfer in Liaoning province, and put forward some suggestions.
